nodes.text: A male Twi'lek served as the security chief aboard Durga the Hutt's Darksaber battlestation. When General Crix Madine infiltrated the superweapon, Durga wanted to execute the Twi'lek, but accidentally executed the Weequay navigator instead. However, he was soon killed along with the rest of the crew when the Darksaber was destroyed in the Hoth asteroid field.
